</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1049368BDF377276C28DFDCEFB0B754C" blockId="85.[151,1436,151,608]" box="[199,1259,583,608]" pageId="85" pageNumber="86">
Etymology. The specific epithet 
<taxonomicName id="D7F64D08DF377276C079FDC0FD887573" authority="Walsingham, 1907" authorityName="Walsingham" authorityYear="1907" box="[563,616,585,608]" class="Insecta" family="Blastobasidae" genus="Hypatopa" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="85" pageNumber="86" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cotis">
