</taxonomicName>
is derived from the Latin 
<emphasis id="2282EA99DF377276C1C6FDC0FC527573" box="[908,946,585,608]" italics="true" pageId="85" pageNumber="86">cos</emphasis>
meaning, a hard flint stone.
</paragraph>
